      <title>热门大宗商品市场困扰着对通胀保持警惕的央行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/commodity-markets-high-gold-oil-copper-prices-will-remain-problem-for-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新的大宗商品繁荣使央行的反通胀努力变得更加复杂，并可能导致短期内大幅降息的前景脱轨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/commodity-markets-high-gold-oil-copper-prices-will-remain-problem-for-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>听证会称，明星主席和前首席执行官密谋推翻监管机构</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/star-chair-and-ex-ceo-plotted-to-oust-regulator-hearing-told</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项调查获悉，星光娱乐集团有限公司的董事长和陷入困境的悉尼赌场运营商的前首席执行官密谋罢免一名政府任命的经理，尽管该公司公开发表了合作声明。该公司股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-15/star-chair-and-ex-ceo-plotted-to-oust-regulator-hearing-told</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Apr 2024 03:41:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
